data.description: Welcome to this charming single-family home in the heart of Indian Land, SC! This well-maintained property boasts 3 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. As you step inside, you’ll be greeted by LVP flooring downstairs with an updated kitchen with modern amenities and fixtures, making meal preparation a breeze. The abundance of natural light throughout the home highlights its warm and inviting atmosphere. The open floor plan allows for seamless flow between the living spaces, perfect for entertaining friends and family. One of the standout features of this home is the large, flat, and private backyard that backs up to a picturesque tree line, offering a serene and peaceful setting for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply unwinding after a long day. In addition to the many attractive features of this property, you’ll also benefit from low HOA fees and taxes, making homeownership more affordable with a Location that is hard to beat!
